Package org.springframework.aot.generate

Class ValueCodeGenerator

java.lang.Object
org.springframework.aot.generate.ValueCodeGenerator
public final class ValueCodeGenerator extends Object
Code generator for a single value. Delegates code generation to a list of configurable ValueCodeGenerator.Delegate implementations.
Since:
6.1.2
Author:
Stephane Nicoll
